race.description: Broncos V Roosters Nrlw Grand Final Hcp (C1)
race.comment: Tricky with resumers engaged and the betting moves will be a guide to the better ones. HOT TORQUE INVEGAS (5) has switched from the Kendrick yard on an 82-day return. Draws out but is proven fresh and benefits from a 3kg claim. Has the ability to win if presented on song. AIN'T TELLIN (4) has switched barns and has also been racing in stronger. Has the rail and 3kg claim and no surprise to see her back on track. SILVER HAMMER (2) is also first up and maps for the run of the race. He also performs fresh and can get into the finish. RED BEAUTY (11) is another resumer who also deserves consideration.
